SELECT ROW_NUMBER() over() as id,"NEIGHBORHOOD" as neighborhood, "SALE PRICE" AS sale_price, "SALE DATE" AS sale_date, "LAND SQUARE FEET" as land_square_feet, "GROSS SQUARE FEET" as gross_square_feet FROM FLOWFILE WHERE "SALE PRICE" <> '-' AND "LAND SQUARE FEET" <> '-' AND "GROSS SQUARE FEET" <> '-'
SELECT id, neighbourhood_group, neighbourhood, latitude, longitude FROM flowfile
SELECT id, name, host_id, host_name, room_type, price, minimum_nights, number_of_reviews, last_review, reviews_per_month, calculated_host_listings_count, availability_365 FROM flowfile

SELECT "Unique ID" as id,Name as name, Measure as measure, "Measure Info" as measure_info, "Geo Place Name" as geo_place_name, "Time Period" as time_period, Start_date as start_date, "Data Value" as data_value FROM FLOWFILE
